data.description: Welcome to the perfect blend of southern charm and coastal living in this renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bath manufactured home just minutes from white sand beaches, NAS Pensacola and local schools and shopping. Spread out across two separate living areas, or get your outdoor toys out of the detached shed and head straight to the beach.  With 2 full bathrooms, wood-burning stove, and fenced-in backyard, this home checks all the boxes while balancing privacy and convenient location close to the community pool, local restaurants and boat launch nearby. Contact your agent or the listing agent to schedule your private walk-through after January 31, 2024. Make this a "must see" on your home shopping list!
